				<td colspan="2"><span>Chardok B does still exists - although I'm usually the only one there on Stromm.  
<br />

<br />
I usually solo the entrance with my necro and there are 2 earrings (one common, one rare) that can drop from the mobs.  The link from Alla's in a previous post points out where you can find these viscous monsters.  And they aren't a walk in the park<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
Having hunted in Chardok B to continue raising my Chardok faction for spirt wracked cords, the appearance of rabids is very rare, but also random.  Some nights I'll get 2 rabids and most other nights none.  The  common earring has dropped for me 5 times and the rare only once.
<br />

<br />
I wasn't aware of this piece specifically except that it allegedly existed.  Now I know I'll be living there more<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
