				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: ChardokB ~ Halls of Betrayal ?<a name="18359"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 2 04 3:44 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Rough and ready guide to getting to the rabid chokidais that drop the necklace:
<br />

<br />
From zone room, head right along the corridor.
<br />
Turn right at the junction, and go past the pens with the live chokidais
<br />
Go past the castle entrance with the 2 golems
<br />

<br />
The room you now find yourself in, with live sarnaks up on the stonework area, is where the necklace chokidais spawn. Kill the mobs in the room till a rabid pops and drops your necklace. The rabids can spawn at any spot in that room except from the live sarnak spawns.
<br />

<br />
Watch out for the mobs that come from the Reanimator room every few minutes.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
